flowchart LR
    A1[Audit Assertion] --> A2[Risk]
    A2 --> A3[Audit Procedure]
    A3 --> A4[Audit Evidence]
    A4 --> A5[Audit Opinion]

    H1[Mission Assertion] --> H2[Failure Mode]
    H2 --> H3[BEAD or Gate Procedure]
    H3 --> H4[Evidence Bundle]
    H4 --> H5[Confidence Gate Decision]

    A1 -.maps to.-> H1
    A2 -.maps to.-> H2
    A3 -.maps to.-> H3
    A4 -.maps to.-> H4
    A5 -.maps to.-> H5
